title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2012 Apr 24 TU [sebaygo1]
description:
.
							
The Peter Schiff Show
Tuesday, 24 April 2012


[sebaygo1]


Tom Woods is guest hosting today's show.

Today's first guest is Tim Carney, Washington Examiner columnist and author of Obamanomics on how conservative coziness with lobbyists undermines free markets.

Today's second guest is Josh Taylor, co-creator of the comedy series Blimey Cow, on how the Internet can elevate an anybody into a somebody.
